# OCTreeTrimming

Reference-based tree-service site localized for Orange County, CA.

## Files

- `index.html` - OCTreeTrimming homepage
- `styles.css` - visual styling
- `scripts/scrape_and_adapt.py` - scraper + adaptation script
- `scraped_text/reference/` - raw extracted text from remartintree.com
- `scraped_text/octreetrimming/` - adapted text for OCTreeTrimming
- `scraped_text/ALL_TEXT_REFERENCE.txt` - full raw merged text
- `scraped_text/ALL_TEXT_OCTREETRIMMING.txt` - full adapted merged text

## Re-run Scrape and Adapt

```bash
python3 scripts/scrape_and_adapt.py
```

This pulls all pages from the source sitemap, extracts visible text, and writes both reference and Orange County adapted outputs.
